00:25:36,790 --> 00:25:37,670
So...

581
00:25:38,630 --> 00:25:39,510
Do you believe him?

582
00:25:40,170 --> 00:25:42,310
My instinct tells me
that he was not lying to me.

583
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:43,400
Yi Yi.

584
00:25:44,080 --> 00:25:45,880
Has your instinct ever worked?

585
00:25:49,020 --> 00:25:49,920
Of course.

586
00:25:50,440 --> 00:25:51,500
My instinct was right about you

587
00:25:51,590 --> 00:25:52,650
and Mr Zhang, wasn't it?

588
00:25:58,160 --> 00:25:59,110
Then,

589
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:01,580
What about Lin Nuo?

590
00:26:02,390 --> 00:26:03,760
Are you breaking up with him?

591
00:26:06,140 --> 00:26:08,160
I never thought about
breaking up with him.

592
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:10,060
Then what about Gu Xiao?

593
00:26:11,890 --> 00:26:13,040
No idea.

594
00:26:14,910 --> 00:26:16,270
But I have forgiven him.

595
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:20,440
You still love him?

596
00:26:23,830 --> 00:26:24,890
I don't know.

597
00:26:25,510 --> 00:26:27,220
Don't ask me such difficult questions.

598
00:26:27,430 --> 00:26:29,250
Will you continue looking
for romantic quotes?

599
00:26:29,340 --> 00:26:30,760
Yes, of course.

600
00:26:30,850 --> 00:26:31,760
Come on, go on.

601
00:26:32,560 --> 00:26:33,270
Take a look.

602
00:26:33,360 --> 00:26:34,400
Next page.

603
00:28:08,520 --> 00:28:09,460
Pretty good.

604
00:28:21,080 --> 00:28:21,960
Worth reading.

605
00:28:22,750 --> 00:28:23,630
Pretty interesting.

606
00:28:23,720 --> 00:28:24,600
Yes.

607
00:28:27,030 --> 00:28:28,080
Very special.

608
00:28:34,280 --> 00:28:35,060
All right.

609
00:28:35,190 --> 00:28:36,320
So what do you think?

610
00:28:36,410 --> 00:28:37,290
Feel free to talk.

611
00:28:38,090 --> 00:28:40,060
I think it's attractive

612
00:28:40,190 --> 00:28:41,760
right from the title.

613
00:28:42,370 --> 00:28:44,740
I think the form is interesting.

614
00:28:45,630 --> 00:28:46,510
Totally agree.

615
00:28:47,230 --> 00:28:48,160
Mei.

616
00:28:48,250 --> 00:28:49,320
My opinion is

617
00:28:49,410 --> 00:28:50,530
that we are well prepared

618
00:28:50,620 --> 00:28:51,680
to publish it serially.

619
00:28:51,770 --> 00:28:53,540
Since everybody agrees,

620
00:28:53,900 --> 00:28:55,220
I now announce that

621
00:28:55,440 --> 00:28:57,920
Perfect And Casual

622
00:28:58,360 --> 00:28:59,900
will be serialized next week.

623
00:29:00,010 --> 00:29:01,310
Nice!

624
00:29:05,980 --> 00:29:06,860
Yun Shu.

625
00:29:07,640 --> 00:29:10,080
Congratulations, you are now officially
a cartoonist.

626
00:29:10,400 --> 00:29:11,170
Mei.

627
00:29:11,260 --> 00:29:12,040
Thank you.

628
00:29:12,150 --> 00:29:13,730
I will do my best.

629
00:29:14,440 --> 00:29:16,130
So it's decided.

630
00:29:33,290 --> 00:29:34,610
[Yun Shu]

631
00:29:35,600 --> 00:29:36,260
Hey.

632
00:29:36,670 --> 00:29:37,770
Mr Zhang

633
00:29:37,860 --> 00:29:39,140
I have a good news for you.

634
00:29:39,230 --> 00:29:39,960
[From next week on,]

635
00:29:40,040 --> 00:29:41,730
[my comic will be formally serialized.]

636
00:29:43,490 --> 00:29:44,370
Congratulations.

637
00:29:45,600 --> 00:29:46,590
Are you busy now?

638
00:29:48,120 --> 00:29:49,320
I'm still at work.

639
00:29:49,460 --> 00:29:50,470
Wait for me at home.

640
00:29:50,570 --> 00:29:51,610
See you this evening.

641
00:30:06,860 --> 00:30:08,310
What are you happy for?

642
00:30:08,790 --> 00:30:09,490
Nothing.

643
00:30:09,800 --> 00:30:10,680
Trifles.

644
00:30:16,060 --> 00:30:17,330
[Yun Shu]

645
00:30:17,540 --> 00:30:18,690
Hello, Sis.

646
00:30:19,230 --> 00:30:20,920
I'm a cartoonist now.

647
00:30:22,210 --> 00:30:23,210
Congratulations.

648
00:30:23,910 --> 00:30:25,970
[A real cartoonist!]

649
00:30:26,390 --> 00:30:27,490
Isn't it awesome?

650
00:30:28,100 --> 00:30:29,430
Yun Shu, I'm a little busy.

651
00:30:29,520 --> 00:30:30,400
Talk to you later.

652
00:30:32,500 --> 00:30:33,570
Fine.

653
00:30:44,100 --> 00:30:44,980
[Hello, Yi Yi.]

654
00:30:45,410 --> 00:30:47,460
[My comic will be serialized next week.]

655
00:30:47,550 --> 00:30:48,430
Awesome, huh?

656
00:30:58,110 --> 00:30:59,090
Congratulations.

657
00:31:00,600 --> 00:31:01,940
I have classes later.

658
00:31:02,030 --> 00:31:02,910
I'm hanging up.

659
00:31:03,430 --> 00:31:04,310
Hey.

660
00:31:16,620 --> 00:31:19,010
Why are they so indifferent?

661
00:31:51,070 --> 00:31:51,950
Cheers.

662
00:31:59,360 --> 00:32:00,240
Wuqian.

663
00:32:00,820 --> 00:32:02,900
I going to tell you a good news.

664
00:32:04,580 --> 00:32:06,070
I, Yun Shu,

665
00:32:06,260 --> 00:32:08,880
have become a real Internet cartoonist.

666
00:32:09,300 --> 00:32:10,550
My comic will

667
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:12,010
be published online next week.

668
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:13,760
And it's serialized.

669
00:32:17,339 --> 00:32:18,839
Actually, I wanted

670
00:32:19,460 --> 00:32:20,390
to celebrate it

671
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:21,930
with Mr Zhang and other friends.

672
00:32:24,010 --> 00:32:25,589
But they are so busy.

673
00:32:26,899 --> 00:32:27,990
Nobody cares.

674
00:32:29,919 --> 00:32:30,890
Congratulations.

675
00:32:31,109 --> 00:32:32,330
You finally became

676
00:32:32,430 --> 00:32:35,060
a real cartoonist as
you've always wanted.

677
00:32:36,140 --> 00:32:37,919
But I have a question.

678
00:32:38,320 --> 00:32:39,879
You must give me the true answer.

679
00:32:41,580 --> 00:32:42,770
Many netizens

680
00:32:42,859 --> 00:32:44,439
are curious as to

681
00:32:44,540 --> 00:32:46,720
why your comic is so sweet.

682
00:32:46,850 --> 00:32:48,540
Is it because you had some

683
00:32:48,620 --> 00:32:51,240
sweet love experiences in your life?

684
00:32:53,120 --> 00:32:55,390
Well, it's a little bit
difficult to answer.

685
00:32:55,770 --> 00:32:57,390
I suddenly

686
00:32:57,710 --> 00:33:00,010
came up with the inspiration

687
00:33:01,669 --> 00:33:04,200
after Mr Zhang forced a kiss on me.

688
00:33:04,980 --> 00:33:06,610
And then I just drew it.

689
00:33:07,160 --> 00:33:08,150
How do you plan to

690
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:09,740
celebrate when Mr Zhang comes back?

691
00:33:09,830 --> 00:33:12,270
I have to think about it properly.

692
00:33:12,360 --> 00:33:13,240
Get ready.

693
00:33:13,590 --> 00:33:14,470
Three.

694
00:33:15,360 --> 00:33:17,170
I will make the first move,

695
00:33:17,270 --> 00:33:18,660
I will tackle him.

696
00:33:23,260 --> 00:33:24,320
Keep your word.

697
00:33:24,410 --> 00:33:25,060
Go.

698
00:33:25,140 --> 00:33:26,880
Of course.

699
00:33:29,730 --> 00:33:30,400
Okay.

700
00:33:30,710 --> 00:33:31,590
Come on.

701
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:35,760
Mr Zhang.

702
00:33:38,730 --> 00:33:40,040
How will you tackle me?

703
00:33:40,530 --> 00:33:42,190
Left or right?

704
00:33:42,330 --> 00:33:43,200
I...

705
00:33:45,200 --> 00:33:46,120
Surprise!

706
00:33:52,260 --> 00:33:57,860
♫ Turning off the lights
in search of its trace ♫

707
00:33:55,590 --> 00:33:56,470
[Dad.]

708
00:33:58,300 --> 00:34:03,710
♫ I walk steadily
on the path beneath my feet ♫

709
00:33:59,440 --> 00:34:02,050
[I've become a real cartoonist.]

710
00:34:02,470 --> 00:34:04,320
[You must be very proud of me, right?]

711
00:34:04,410 --> 00:34:10,130
♫ I hear someone asking,
are you still here? ♫

712
00:34:04,800 --> 00:34:07,570
[Thank you for encouraging
me when I was little,]

713
00:34:07,870 --> 00:34:09,760
[taking care of me and supporting me.]

714
00:34:10,080 --> 00:34:11,820
[I have something to share.]

715
00:34:10,480 --> 00:34:15,980
♫ The kind person replies,
I've always been here ♫

716
00:34:11,940 --> 00:34:13,780
[I met the biggest hurdle

717
00:34:13,870 --> 00:34:15,920
in my career.]

718
00:34:16,350 --> 00:34:18,800
[A nemesis and enemy.]

719
00:34:16,510 --> 00:34:19,550
♫ This love cuts through the crowd
in search of me ♫

720
00:34:19,240 --> 00:34:22,450
[Mr Zhang forces me to do math]

721
00:34:20,250 --> 00:34:22,060
♫ It isn't easy ♫

722
00:34:22,230 --> 00:34:25,440
♫ I only wish to cherish it with you ♫

723
00:34:22,540 --> 00:34:23,770
[with a cold face every day.]

724
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:25,350
[He always criticizes me.]

725
00:34:25,870 --> 00:34:28,220
[I never heard good
words from him.]

726
00:34:26,320 --> 00:34:27,820
♫ Each and every moment ♫

727
00:34:28,700 --> 00:34:33,720
♫ If I missed out, I will meet you again
in another lifetime ♫

728
00:34:30,120 --> 00:34:31,000
[But,]

729
00:34:32,690 --> 00:34:34,930
[Dad, do you know?]

730
00:34:34,510 --> 00:34:40,670
♫ I recognise your eyes,
a secret that belongs to me ♫

731
00:34:35,730 --> 00:34:38,430
[Although he looks cold and unfeeling,]

732
00:34:40,660 --> 00:34:42,630
[he is actually]

733
00:34:44,840 --> 00:34:46,090
[a warm person.]

734
00:34:47,650 --> 00:34:49,670
[It's him who has always been encouraging]

735
00:34:49,760 --> 00:34:50,810
[and supporting me.]

736
00:34:53,110 --> 00:34:54,400
[He made me]

737
00:34:55,660 --> 00:34:57,370
[who I am right now.]

738
00:34:58,040 --> 00:35:00,500
[Though, it's not solely his credit.]

739
00:35:01,030 --> 00:35:03,800
[My sister,]

740
00:35:04,470 --> 00:35:09,440
♫ The night will pass,
I am the dawn ♫

741
00:35:04,520 --> 00:35:05,400
[grandpa,]

742
00:35:05,530 --> 00:35:06,410
[Yi Yi]

743
00:35:06,920 --> 00:35:07,800
[and Lin Nuo.]

744
00:35:08,380 --> 00:35:10,220
[have been with me.]

745
00:35:10,370 --> 00:35:15,730
♫ Protecting this innocence,
evident in your eyes ♫

746
00:35:11,790 --> 00:35:12,890
[I'm really]

747
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:14,900
[blessed to have them.]

748
00:35:15,350 --> 00:35:16,280
[So Dad,]

749
00:35:16,660 --> 00:35:21,850
♫ I hear someone asking,
do dreams come to an end? ♫

750
00:35:17,740 --> 00:35:18,760
[please don't worry.]

751
00:35:19,380 --> 00:35:22,060
[Sister and I are all very happy.]

752
00:35:22,590 --> 00:35:28,220
♫ I will keep you company in
the future, never letting go ♫

753
00:35:28,540 --> 00:35:31,830
♫ This love cuts through the crowd
in search of me ♫

754
00:35:32,150 --> 00:35:33,820
♫ It doesn't make sense ♫

755
00:35:34,260 --> 00:35:37,900
♫ All I can do is silently
feel your breath ♫

756
00:35:38,140 --> 00:35:40,100
♫ And take you in my arms ♫

757
00:35:41,830 --> 00:35:45,920
[Easter Egg Time]

758
00:35:47,690 --> 00:35:49,390
I think the name...

759
00:35:49,980 --> 00:35:51,880
I think it's good.

760
00:35:52,980 --> 00:35:54,530
Call me that in the future.

761
00:35:55,290 --> 00:35:56,870
Do not call me Mr Zhang anymore.

762
00:35:59,810 --> 00:36:01,880
But... Mr Zhang,

763
00:36:01,970 --> 00:36:04,890
I can't bring myself
to call you that.

764
00:36:06,170 --> 00:36:07,350
Then practise.

765
00:36:07,820 --> 00:36:08,700
Practise?

766
00:36:09,410 --> 00:36:10,710
Until you can say it.

767
00:36:14,290 --> 00:36:15,440
Mr Zhang.

768
00:36:18,350 --> 00:36:19,360
Honey.

769
00:36:20,610 --> 00:36:21,950
Honey...
